    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Cavalier/Samurai Order Abilitiy</strong><br/><br/><p>At 2nd level, when the cavalier deals damage to an opponent with his Hellknight order's favored weapon, as a swift action he learns whether that creature's alignment is chaotic, as if he had cast detect chaos and studied the creature for 3 rounds. Additionally, if he learns that a creature is chaotic by using this ability, he gains a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls against it. This bonus does not stack with itself, but it does stack with the bonus from the cavalier's challenge.</p>",
